metadata.name: Purgatory
metadata.description:
Digital Planet 1: Purgatory. Caught between the top and bottom of life - this character, Mo, is indifferent. Rather than a halo, a question mark lies on his head signifying his unbothered existence. Oddly enough, in indifference, ultimately we find peace. 

This 1/1 digital planet includes an AR sculpture. What could these 3d planets be building?

Zoe Winters. 1/1 3D sculpt and animation. 2022
